message.body: Food trucks around here are a lot like corner stores in South Philly in terms of quality and price.
Penn kids are lucky but a lot of them probably wouldn't eat from a cart.
I know. They're stupid. Food trucks need to go through all the licences and inspections that restaurants do. What are they afraid of?
That sandwich looks good.
I know haha I meant to take a picture before I bit it but I was too hungry
Haha. That's ok.

So I was gonna fax my information to that person at Penn as soon as possible. But I think I should wait until after next week when I get my ACLS certification so I can put it on my resume. Do you think so too? There aren't any positions open right now anyway that I would want.
Yeah that's probably best
Ok!
By the way, I called Penn Benefits to ask about retirement
They don't start matching for me until May 1.
:/ Ok. But are you going to sign up before then?
I could have signed up before, but all that would've been was me putting money myself aside. But I'm saving anyway already
Ok then. I will remind you again come May first!
I can sign up before then but have to decide if I want Roth or not
Eh. I always forget the difference.
It has to do with pretax or post tax
Yeah. I know that. Well, you have time to think about it then.
Yeah I know

What the hell. Peekaboo actually let me pet her in the window without snapping. Then she jumps out of the window, which makes the blinds smack me in the face, and then she jumps down from the tv right into the kibble bowl and spills it. Ugh!
Haha her payback
Oh my god! I just got a message from Penn endocrine associates. They want to interview me Tuesday at 12! I have to call her back when I have time.
It's an outpatient job. I remember applying to endocrine associates but I don't remember it being called a triage nurse. But I totally want interview and see what it entails!
Ooh my god! I'm nervous! It could be bad timing with me trying get into Jeff! But I want outpatient. And it's penn!
I work Tuesday. If that's the only day they can do it, I call out right?
Yes definitely!
That's great
Maybe don't call out but try to move
I'm happy for you!
Yeah. I'll ask for Monday or Wednesday first.
Oh baby. I gotta get back to work. But I'll text mor later. I can't wait to be able to talk to you!
Once you started working, you were 2 for 2 with the interview/acceptance ratio
You're gonna do fine :)
Me too. I want to hear more.
Love you!
I love you too
I hate this though. I'm all weak and shaky and I gotta go out there and play it cool. I need to tell Davida! That will calm me down. Talk to you later!
I love you too
Haha okay.
Talk to you later
Ok! So Tuesday it is!
Okay cool
